---
const videoSrc = '/SegundoVideo.mp4';

---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/Logo.svg" />
    <title>Ups, Pagina no Encontrada</title>
</head>
<body class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center w-full h-screen bg-slate-900 text-white font-roboto">
   
<article class="w-full h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center p-10">
  

    <h3 class="md:text-4xl text-2xl font-bold text-center font-Oswald text-white">
      Ups, Parece que te perdiste
    </h3>
  
    <section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 md:w-[55%] max-w-4xl h-auto gap-10 p-4 sm:p-10 items-center shadow-2xl rounded-xl">
  
      <video 
        class=" w-[450px] h-[250px]  rounded-lg shadow-lg object-cover" 
        preload="metadata" muted autoplay loop>
        <source src={videoSrc} type="video/mp4" />
        Tu navegador no soporta la reproducción de videos.
      </video>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-evenly gap-10">
        <p class="font-roboto text-justify md:text-xl sm:text-base">
          ¿Pero aun asi, porque no vuelves a nuestra pagina principal?
          <span class="mt-10 text-orange-600 font-bold font-roboto">TE ESTAMOS ESPERANDO</span>
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/" 
          class="p-3 text-sm sm:text-lg bg-orange-700 text-white font-Oswald rounded-lg shadow-xl text-center hover:bg-orange-600 duration-300">
          SALA DE TÉ LA ROMANA
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
    
</body>
</html>